metadata.name: Unravel People's SAND33
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's SAND33, which represents an inactive state of pSAND33. User can participate in a new bundle of 3X3 Sandbox lands acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's SAND33 as credit. upSAND33 can be claimed into pSAND33 when the subscription successfully acquires a new bundle of 3X3 Sandbox lands.
